===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-prison.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪzən|-ɪzən]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''prison''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]''; ''plural'' '''prisons''')

#A place of long-term confinement for those convicted of serious crimes.
#:''The cold stone walls of the prison had stood for over a century.''
#{{uncountable}} Confinement in a prison.
#:''Prison was a harrowing experience for him.''

====Synonyms====
*(''place''): [[jail]], [[gaol]] (''old-fashioned British'').  See [[Wikisaurus:jail]].
*(''confinement''): [[imprisonment]]

